021400******************************************************************02140000
021500* PROCESS THE UPDATE FILE. IF A RECORD IS READ, GATHER WHATEVER   02150000
021600* OTHER DATA IS NECESSARY TO TAKE CHECKPOINTS BASED ON THE TYPE OF02160000
021700* CHECKPOINTS BEING TAKEN BY EPKUP102 AND ISSUE A WRITE REQUEST   02170000
021800* TO THE TRANSACTION PREPARATION PROGRAM.                         02180000
021900******************************************************************02190000
022000 B100-PROCESS-UPDATE-INPUT-FILE.                                  02200000
022100                                                                  02210000
022200     IF FIRST-TRANS-READ                                          02220000
022300         MOVE EP004-INTR-UPC-ID TO PV-INTR-UPC-ID                 02230000
022400         MOVE 'N'               TO PS-FIRST-TRANS-READ-SW         02240000
022500     END-IF.                                                      02250000
022600                                                                  02260000
022700     IF CONTROL-BREAK                                             02270000
022800         PERFORM C300-CKPT-BY-CNTL-BREAK                          02280000
022900     ELSE                                                         02290000
023000         IF LOGICAL-TRANSACTION                                   02300000
023100             PERFORM C400-CKPT-BY-LOGICAL-TRANS                   02310000
023200         ELSE                                                     02320000
023300             PERFORM C500-CKPT-BY-TIME-OR-REQUEST                 02330000
023400         END-IF                                                   02340000
023500     END-IF.                                                      02350000
023600                                                                  02360000
023700     PERFORM C200-READ-UPDATE-INPUT-FILE.                         02370000
023800                                                                  02380000
023900                                                                  02390000
